abstract: >-
  Founder-Ops is an open-source AI-powered operating system for startup
  founders. Built on Claude Code, it provides 40 specialist modes, 22
  playbooks, and 13 scoring frameworks covering customer discovery,
  prioritization, fundraising, growth, hiring, finance, positioning,
  content, operations, and founder wellbeing.
